diff --git a/CHANGELOG.md b/CHANGELOG.md
index 435c7878..f40cd148 100644
--- a/CHANGELOG.md
+++ b/CHANGELOG.md
@@ -36,6 +36,8 @@ At this point in time, it is not yet decided what the next steps will be. Ktlint
 
 ### Removed
 
+* Drop support for `ktlint-disable` and `ktlint-enable` comment-based directives. Use `@Suppress` annotations instead. A new rule `no-deprecated-ktlint-directive` is added to detect and report usage of these deprecated directives.
+
 ### Fixed
 
 * Do not flag a (potential) mutable extension property in case the getter is annotated or prefixed with a modifier `property-naming` ([#2024](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/issues/2024))
